data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Your Dream Home in Riverview, Happy Acres! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and elegance in this stunningly remodeled home nestled in the serene Riverview subdivision of Happy Acres. Boasting an expansive layout, this property features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, making it ideal for a large family or accommodating a mother-in-law suite. Key Features include Spacious Living with 4 well-appointed bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation and privacy. 3 Modern Bathrooms elegantly designed with top-of-the-line fixtures. Beautiful newly installed tile and laminate flooring throughout the home. Every inch of this home has been updated with high-quality finishes and contemporary touches. The layout is perfect for family gatherings and offers separate spaces for multigenerational living. This home is more than just a living space; it’s a haven for creating lasting memories. The Riverview subdivision offers a friendly community atmosphere, making it an ideal place to grow and thrive. Don’t Miss Out: This exceptional property is a rare find in Happy Acres and won’t be on the market for long. Schedule your private showing today and take the first step towards making this dream home your reality!
